EXPLORE EACH ROOM (SPECTRUM VERSION)

When you press ENTER to start the game, hold down the keys O, A, P and C until Dizzy disappears.
You can then move around the screens using Z, X, K and M.
Press SPACE to re-appear on the chosen screen.

EXPLORE EACH ROOM (AMSTRAD VERSION)

On the title screen, hold down the keys C, A, P, S and SPACE, and don’t release until Dizzy starts moving.
Press C and then Dizzy will disappear, you can now move around the screens using the buttons Z, X, K and M.
Press SPACE to re-appear on the chosen screen.
OTHER CHEATS (AMIGA AND ATARI ST VERSIONS ONLY)

– During gameplay, type ‘EGGONASPRING‘ to toggle extra high jumps.
– During gameplay, type ‘EGGSONLEGS‘ to toggle immunity to everything except cage traps.
– During gameplay, type ‘ICANFLY‘ to toggle flight mode.

